        "subject": "LU-0000 test: test should not assume same path",
        "message": "LU-0000 test: test should not assume same path\n\nOn EL7, /sbin is symlinked to /usr/sbin. Tests\nshould not assume all nodes running the same distro\nand have the same path to commands (ie. lctl)\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <minh.diep@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I21ae9a0689634e5ec01da0da5b586c0376cee2e7\n"
